high_descs: Move to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the wooden round table.
Slice the tomato on the wooden round table.
Set the knife down on the wooden round table.
Pick up a tomato slice on the wooden round table.
Turn right twice and move to the kitchen sink.
Place the tomato slice in to the bowl in the sink.
Pick up the bowl in the sink with the tomato slice in it.
Turn around and move towards the microwave at the end of the counter.
Place the bowl with the tomato slice into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a tomato slice into the microwave.
